; =============================================================================
; TemplateMod.def – Module Definition File
; =============================================================================
; This File is OPTIONAL. It only is needed, if the own DLL has
; functions that are to be exported (for example if other tools should recognize your Mod).
;
; For a clean Injection-Mod is this file NOT needed – the Mod-Code runs through
; your DllMain/DLL_PROCESS_ATTACH, which does not need any exports.
;
; If you need exports (for example for an API that calls other mods):
;   1. Add your function names under EXPORTS
;   2. Add this .def File to the Linker-Settings:
;      Project > Properties > Linker > Input > Moduledefinitionfile
; =============================================================================

LIBRARY TemplateMod
EXPORTS
    ; Add your own exports here for example:
    ; GetModInfo
